 《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》似乎改变了游戏中爱情的运作方式https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/persona-3-reload-seemingly-shifts-how-romances-will-work-in-the-game-3493484?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=persona- 3-重新加载看似转变的浪漫故事将如何在游戏中发挥作用Imogen DonovanTue, 05 Sep 2023 13:34:16 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3493484 <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p>这并不是重制版中唯一的现代化改造</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/persona-3-reload-seemingly-shifts-how-romances-will-work-in-the-game-3493484">《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》的帖子似乎改变了游戏中爱情的运作方式，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/persona-3-reload"><em>《女神异闻录 3：重装版》</em></a>似乎正在改变重制版中的浪漫故事，以使这一特殊机制成为一种选择。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/persona-3-reload-preview-hands-on-gameplay-3490210">《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》预览：黑暗时刻看起来比以往任何时候都更好</a></strong></li></ul><p>社交链接（原版《女神异闻<em>录 3》</em>中的浪漫术语）一旦社交链接达到最高水平，就会自动与 Fuuka、Mitsura 和 Yukari 建立关系。然而， <a href="https://imdaonline.imda.gov.sg/classification/Search/VideoGames/MoreInfo.aspx?sTitle=IDX/2309/000251" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新加坡信息通信媒体发展局的一项分类</a>表明，玩家将能够拒绝浪漫的求爱。</p><p> <em><a href="https://noisypixel.net/persona-3-reload-optional-romances/?expand_article=1&amp;utm_content=cmp-true" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Noisy Pixel</a></em>发现，该分类指出“当玩家充分建立男性主角与某些女性角色的联系时，可能会出现可选的人物拥抱和亲吻的描述，以及暗示性亲密的文字描述”。</p><p>有关<em>《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》</em>的信息还补充说，游戏中的女性角色将以性感的方式展现。 “有些对话包含对女性角色的服装和外表的暗示性暗示。女性角色在战斗中可以穿着比基尼般的盔甲，露出部分臀部、腹部和乳沟，”分类继续说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3493510" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3493510" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3493510" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/persona-3-reload-social-links-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3493510" class="wp-caption-text"> 《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》来源：世嘉</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/persona-4"><em>《女神异闻录 4》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/persona-5"><em>《女神异闻录 5》</em></a>允许玩家拒绝同伴角色的进步，即使已达到最大关系级别，因此<em>《女神异闻录 3》</em>的改版版似乎也会采用相同的做法。</p><p>如果是这样的话，它并不是<em>《女神异闻录 3：重装版》</em>中唯一带回的现代元素。在<em>NME</em>即将推出的角色扮演游戏预览中，添加了<em>《女神异闻录 5》</em>的接力棒传递机制，以实现更直观的战斗。</p><p>考虑到这一点，预览版“重点关注与前两款<em>《女神异</em>闻录》游戏基本相同的战斗”，因此粉丝们仍在等待新的辰巳港岛这次会提供什么。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sony">索尼</a>互动娱乐美国公司前总裁兼首席执行官表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/former-playstation-boss-claims-google-amazon-apple-greatest-threats-gaming-3493336">游戏面临的最大威胁是谷歌、亚马逊和苹果等公司的蚕食</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/persona-3-reload-seemingly-shifts-how-romances-will-work-in-the-game-3493484">《女神异闻录 3：重装上阵》的帖子似乎改变了游戏中爱情的运作方式，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Chvrches 的 Lauren Mayberry 翻唱了麦当娜，并在首场现场表演中首次亮相https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-madonna-and-debuts-solo-material-at-first-live-show-footage-setlist-3493492?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-madonna-and-debuts-solo-material-at-first-live-show-footage-setlistLiberty Dunworth Tue, 05 Sep 2023 12:53:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3493492 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) 将于 2023 年演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>音乐会在这位音乐家正式发行她的首张单曲几天后举行</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-madonna-and-debuts-solo-material-at-first-live-show-footage-setlist-3493492">Chvrches 的 Lauren Mayberry 翻唱了麦当娜，并在首次现场表演中首次亮相，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) 将于 2023 年演出" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Lauren-Mayberry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chvrches">Chvrches</a>的主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lauren-mayberry">Lauren Mayberry</a>首次以独唱艺术家身份进行现场表演，并首次推出了一些前所未闻的作品。在下面查找演出的片段和完整的曲目列表。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/chvrches-mad-cool-2022-karaoke-bangers-robert-smith-decade-together-3264219">Chvrches at Mad Cool 2022 卡拉 OK 歌曲、Robert Smith 和十年的合作</a></strong></li></ul><p>首场演出于昨晚（9 月 4 日）在华盛顿特区的 9:30 俱乐部举行，这标志着这位歌手首次以独唱艺术家的身份登上头条节目。</p><p>它也是在这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-makes-solo-debut-with-piano-ballad-are-you-awake-3491767">正式发行她的首张单曲</a>——情感、亲密的民谣《Are You Awake》三天后发布的。梅伯里与加拿大歌手兼作曲家小托拜厄斯·杰索<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tobias-jesso-jr">(Tobias Jesso Jr)</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zedd">Zedd 的</a>合作者马修·科马 (Matthew Koma) 合作创作了这首歌，马修·科马也担任这首歌的制作人。</p><p>昨晚的现场表演拉开帷幕，梅伯里以一首名为“Bird”的歌曲开场，这是一首乐观、态度驱动的歌曲，当她唱着“<em>让我们宣传我们的幸福</em>/<em>或在至少我会强颜欢笑”</em> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lauren Mayberry (Chvrches) 现场 - Bird - 9:30 Club, DC - 9/4/23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/47yfpj56N5w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>从那时起，她开始创作一首名为“Shame”的歌曲，在这首歌曲中，她充满活力，从直率、对抗性的副歌进入庄严、更平静的时刻。</p><p>接下来是舞蹈主题曲“Change Shapes”，随后是更黑暗、性感的新歌“Mantra”。查找下面歌曲的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2/9 Lauren Mayberry - 耻辱（首次表演！）@ 9:30 俱乐部，华盛顿特区 9/04/23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aDeJuqhbgwI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lauren Mayberry - 改变形状（9:30 俱乐部，华盛顿特区 9/4/23）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eukurSSGg_U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="劳伦·梅伯里 - 咒语（现场）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bpvhIT9aVOY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在这场突破性的演出中首次现场亮相的其他曲目包括一首名为“Under The Knife”的歌曲、一首名为“Crocodile Tears”的 80 年代流行歌曲以及一首充满活力的流行朋克歌曲“Sorry, Etc.”，演出的结束曲。</p><p>虽然绝大多数曲目都是梅伯里新个人专辑中以前从未听过的曲目，但她确实将她最近分享的首张单曲《Are You Awake》作为当晚的倒数第二首曲目进行了演绎——坐在键盘后面这样做。她还翻唱了 1989 年麦当娜的经典歌曲《Like A Prayer》，给歌迷带来了惊喜。在下面查找更多片段和曲目列表。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="劳伦·梅伯里 (Lauren Mayberry) - 鳄鱼之泪 (9:30 Club, Washington D.C. 9/4/23)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hVLP2GXygSA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lauren Mayberry - 抱歉等等（9:30 俱乐部，华盛顿特区，2023 年 9 月 4 日）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NQlSSwQFZpM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lauren Mayberry (Chvrches) 现场 - Like a Prayer (麦当娜封面) - 9:30 Club, DC - 9/4/23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aJHfTRz1Mzo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lauren Mayberry - 你醒着吗（9:30 俱乐部，华盛顿特区 9/4/23）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EsMl6cHunqQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2><strong>劳伦·梅伯里饰演：</strong></h2><p> <strong>&#39;鸟&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;耻辱&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“改变形状”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;咒语&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>《刀下》</strong><br /> <strong>《鳄鱼的眼泪》</strong><br /> <strong>《Like A Prayer》（麦当娜封面）</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;你醒着么？&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“对不起，等等。”</strong></p><p>在上周发布突破性的个人歌曲之前，梅伯里宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-launches-fun-freaky-sad-weird-joyful-solo-career-with-tour-3471192">她的首次个人巡演</a>，并用 30 秒的预览<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-previews-debut-solo-single-are-you-awake-3483022">来预告这首单曲</a>。</p><p>当时，她还在社交媒体上分享说，当谈到即将到来的个人首秀时，她“在兴奋和极度恐惧之间摇摆不定”。 “我从来没有真正想过我会写一首钢琴民谣，或者一张个人专辑句号，所以生活真的充满了惊喜，”她说。 “我真的很期待这一章，迫不及待地想让人们听到更多的音乐。”</p><p>在《你醒着吗？》发行之前梅伯里的个人作品很少。她为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/death-cab-for-cutie">Death Cab for Cutie 的</a>歌曲《Northern Lights》客串演唱，该歌曲收录在他们 2018 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/death-cab-cutie-thank-today-album-review-2366912">《Thank You For Today》</a>中。</p><p>她还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-dessner">Aaron Dessner</a>合作翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frightened-rabbit">Frightened Rabbit</a>的“Who&#39;d Kill You Now?”为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/death-cab-for-cutie-ben-gibbard-reflects-tribute-show-frightened-rabbit-scott-hutchison-rough-trade-nyc-2417398">乐队已故主唱</a>斯科特·哈钦森 (Scott Hutchinson) 制作的纪念专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/various-artists-tiny-changes-a-celebration-of-frightened-rabbits-the-midnight-organ-fight-2526196">《Tiny Changes》</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3491768" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3491768" style="width: 1999px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3491768" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg" alt="" width="1999" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello.jpg 1999w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Lauren-Mayberry-Scarlett-Casciello-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3491768" class="wp-caption-text">劳伦·梅伯里。图片来源：斯嘉丽·卡西洛。</figcaption></figure><p>梅伯里的个展将于今晚（9 月 5 日）继续在华盛顿特区的 The Anthem 举行。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Flauren-mayberry-tickets%2Fartist%2F3036567" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>查找所有即将到来的巡演日期和任何剩余的门票。</p><p>至于 Chvrches，该乐队最新的录音室专辑是 2021 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/chvrches-screen-violence-review-3029924">《Screen Violence》</a> ，然而，苏格兰合成流行三重奏目前正准备发行首张录音室专辑 2013 年的《The Bones Of What You Believe》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-share-unheard-song-manhattan-announce-10th-anniversary-bones-of-what-you-believe-3483993">10 周年纪念再版。</a> 。</p><p>新版本包括四首前所未闻的歌曲和五首 2013 年的现场录音，将于 10 月 13 日发行。</p><p>后<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chvrches-lauren-mayberry-covers-madonna-and-debuts